title: ASMR Treats from Australia! *Crinkles and Soft-Spoken Happiness*
description: Many thanks to Nick for his kindness and generosity! I very much enjoyed all of the foods and gifts you sent to me :) **EDIT** I've just realized what it is that Vegemite reminds me of!!! It reminds me a lot of jajang, which is this Korean blackbean sauce that is normally eaten on noodles (jajangmyeon) or rice (jajangbap). I love me some jajang, so that's probably why I liked the flavor of Vegemite ^_^ This is a little bit different from my regular videos, but in this video, I will be tasting foods from Australia that I've never ever tried before! I hope it is at least entertaining haha, and maybe you'll get some tingles too ^_^ If you would like to send me foods or fun things from where you live, here is my address!
